<div class="container-map">
  <div class="text-map">
    <h1>Find a rat near you</h1>
    <p>What makes being a fancy rat even better?  <br>Being a fancy rat with friends!  <br>See below which rats live nearby so you can invite them to your next fashionable soiree.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="map-item">
    <div id="map"
        style="width: 100%; height: 600px;"
        data-markers="<%= @markers.to_json %>"
        data-mapbox-api-key="<%= ENV['MAPBOX_API_KEY'] %>">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
